               class=``list-description'' style=``margin-left: 24px;''><p
               id=``p0025'' style=``margin-bottom: 16px;''>Considering
               vegetation cover and soil properties is crucial to understanding
               spectral diversity.</p></dd></dl><p></p></div>",
  keywords  = "Biodiversity; Spectral diversity; Ecology; Sentinel-2;
